longDescription.value: Choose a Design-a-Side® (DAS) to fit your interests. If you select School Mascot, your ring will feature your school's chosen mascot symbol (not available on Sheer Ice design). If available, additional charge applies for NASCAR, NHL, NFL, NHRA and IHRA. All logos are officially licensed by applicable organization in the US and US territories only-additional restrictions may apply. Not available to international customers.

longDescription.value: Enter the text you want it to appear on the inside of your ring (i.e., SRS). Engraving will be done in UPPERCASE!

The inside of your ring will be engraved with script lettering. If you choose Full Name, the engraving will be done exactly as you type it. If you choose Initials, the engraving will be done in UPPERCASE! Orders with inappropriate or offensive language will be refused.
